name: Killamari

ability.name: Fried Squid
ability.description:
While in team, can be summoned and used instead of a glider.
Can float for long periods of time while gliding.

description: It wraps itself around an enemy's head, sucking out their insides. Pal mummies are occasionally found, but these are in fact Killamari victims.

skills.name: Hydro Jet
skills.description: Hurls a high speed ball of water at an enemy.

skills.name: Poison Blast
skills.description: Hurls poison sludge at an enemy.

skills.name: Dark Ball
skills.description: Unleashes a sphere of darkness that slowly tracks down the enemy.

skills.name: Shadow Burst
skills.description: Quickly discharges dark energy, damaging those around it.

skills.name: Acid Rain
skills.description: Creates acidic clouds that pour down acid rain on enemies.

skills.name: Nightmare Ball
skills.description: Creates a giant ball of darkness and hurls it at an enemy.

skills.name: Dark Laser
skills.description: Charges dark energy before blasting enemies with a powerful beam.
